:  The visual property of objects.

## Math

Inline $`E = mc^2` stays crisp; display math gets its own block:

$$`\int_0^1 x\,dx = \tfrac{1}{2}`

## Inline extras

A hard line break ends this line\
and continues on the next. An inline span carries attributes:
[flagged]{.featured #note-1}. Smart typography turns "quotes", -- dashes, and
... into typographic forms automatically.

## Admonitions

::: note
Heads up - canonical types render as `<aside class="admonition note">`.
:::

::: tip "Pro Tip"
A quoted title becomes an `admonition-title`.
:::

::: hint "Custom"
A non-canonical type renders as a generic `<div>` with that class.
:::

